<%# The three-layer measurement stack: MTA, MMM, Incrementality. %>
<%# Each layer has a different cadence and role. The arrows between layers show how data and calibration flow. %>

<figure class="my-12 not-prose">
  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">

    <%# Header %>
    <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pt-8 pb-6 border-b border-slate-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">The Three-Layer Measurement Stack</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm sm:text-base mt-1">Each method runs at a different cadence and answers a different question. Together they triangulate.</p>
    </div>

    <%# Stack body %>
    <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 py-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50/60 to-white">

      <%# Top layer — Incrementality %>
      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white border-l-4 border-amber-400 rounded-md px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 sm:py-5">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
            <span class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-amber-300 tracking-[0.15em]">LAYER 3</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold">Incrementality</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 tracking-wide">CADENCE &middot; QUARTERLY+</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-200 italic mb-3">Causal proof. Ground truth.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-200">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Geo holdouts and randomized tests</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Resolves MTA/MMM disputes when methods disagree</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-400 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Calibrates both layers below with experimental evidence</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <%# Connector — Incrementality ↔ MMM %>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-1 sm:gap-3 py-2 text-[11px] sm:text-xs text-slate-500">
        <svg class="rotate-90 sm:rotate-0 shrink-0" width="36" height="14" viewBox="0 0 36 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M 6 7 L 30 7" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
          <path d="M 6 3 L 2 7 L 6 11" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
          <path d="M 30 3 L 34 7 L 30 11" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
        </svg>
        <span class="italic"><strong class="not-italic font-semibold text-slate-700">calibrates</strong> MMM coefficients with causal evidence</span>
      </div>

      <%# Middle layer — MMM %>
      <div class="bg-indigo-100 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 rounded-md px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 sm:py-5">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
            <span class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-indigo-600 tracking-[0.15em]">LAYER 2</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">MMM</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-mono text-indigo-700 tracking-wide">CADENCE &middot; QUARTERLY</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-indigo-700 italic mb-3">Strategic allocation. Privacy-resilient.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-500 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Budget split across channels</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-500 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Saturation curves and carryover effects</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-indigo-500 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Includes offline channels MTA can't see (TV, OOH, podcast)</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <%# Connector — MMM ↔ MTA %>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-1 sm:gap-3 py-2 text-[11px] sm:text-xs text-slate-500">
        <svg class="rotate-90 sm:rotate-0 shrink-0" width="36" height="14" viewBox="0 0 36 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M 6 7 L 30 7" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
          <path d="M 6 3 L 2 7 L 6 11" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
          <path d="M 30 3 L 34 7 L 30 11" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
        </svg>
        <span class="italic">
          <strong class="not-italic font-semibold text-slate-700">MTA conversions</strong> feed MMM as inputs &middot;
          <strong class="not-italic font-semibold text-slate-700">MMM</strong> reweights MTA channel attribution
        </span>
      </div>

      <%# Bottom layer — MTA %>
      <div class="bg-slate-100 border-l-4 border-slate-400 rounded-md px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 sm:py-5">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
            <span class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 tracking-[0.15em]">LAYER 1</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">MTA</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 tracking-wide">CADENCE &middot; DAILY / WEEKLY</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 italic mb-3">Tactical optimization. Digital channels.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-slate-500 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Pause/scale campaigns and creatives</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-slate-500 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Customer journey analysis (paths, drop-offs)</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-slate-500 shrink-0">&middot;</span><span>Real-time ROAS and channel-level performance</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%# Footer takeaway %>
    <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-slate-900">When two layers agree, you have confidence. When they disagree, you have a research question.</strong>
        Incrementality tests are how you answer it &mdash; and the answer flows back down to recalibrate the layers below.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
  <figcaption class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 text-center">
    Framework: mbuzz &middot; Cadences reflect typical practice at $500K&ndash;$5M annual marketing spend
  </figcaption>
</figure>
